Note:
Runa Natural Language Bytecode Integration Test

This test validates that the bytecode and VM correctly handle natural language operators
and that the compiler can generate proper bytecode for Runa's natural language syntax.

Test Coverage:
- Natural language arithmetic operators (plus, minus, multiplied by, divided by)
- Natural language comparison operators (is greater than, is equal to, etc.)
- Natural language logic operators (logical and, logical or)
- Natural language bitwise operators (bitwise and, shifted left by)
- Bytecode generation and execution
- Type coercion between Integer and Float
:End Note

Note: Import dependencies
Import "../../../src/compiler/driver.runa"
Import "../../../src/modules/stdlib/stubs/core_types.runa"

