Note: Test Runner
Process called "main":
    Note: Main test runner
    Let result be run_natural_language_bytecode_tests
    
    If result.success:
        Print "🎉 All Natural Language Bytecode Tests PASSED!"
        Print "✅ Bytecode correctly handles natural language operators"
        Exit with code 0
    Otherwise:
